uantum Calogero-Moser system associated\nto $N$-point spherical functions are also common eigenfunctions of a commuting\nfamily of first-order differential operators, which we call asymptotic boundary\nKnizhnik-Zamolodchikov-Bernard operators. These operators are explicitly given\nin terms of $\\theta$-folded classical dynamical $r$-matrices and associated\ndynamical $k$-matrices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 13:34:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 10:27:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 2 May 2020 10:36:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 08:53:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-05"}
