Sat, the accurate pointing\nprecision required for the lasercom link, and the difficulties of closing the\nlink at such a high speed as 10 Gbit/s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 11:37:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-10"}
